+# Module 1 ¬∑ Lessons 02‚Äì07 Storyboards and Slides
+
+Updated: 2026-06-02 15:20 CEST
+
+**Scope:** Compact storyboard/slide plan for Module 1 MVP lessons 2‚Äì7.
+
+**Production rule:** Visuals support the lesson scene only. No UI reskin, no childish mascot energy, no fake German text inside generated images. Boss narration stays Malayalam/Manglish; on-screen text stays low and proofread.
+
+---
+
+## Shared visual style for Lessons 02‚Äì07
+
+- Adult Malayali learner, Kerala home/classroom/Goethe Kochi practice context.
+- Warm but serious exam-prep mood.
+- Simple teacher/video-call frames for Frau Weber.
+- One German line or one tiny table at a time.
+- Phone-friendly crops: face + phrase card, not dense whiteboard.
+- Use clocks, reception desks, audio cards, and tiny dialogue bubbles to compress explanation.
+- Avoid: mascot chatter, game badges, feature grids, big roadmaps, generic Germany stock landmarks.
+
+---
+
+## Lesson 02 ‚Äî Why A1 Matters for Malayalis
+
+### Slide/scene sequence
+
+1. **A1 is the first survival level**
+   - Visual: Kerala learner opening app; one `Goethe A1` card.
+   - Text: `A1 = first German survival level.`
+   - Talking head: Boss gives short Manglish framing.
+
+2. **Four exam skills**
+   - Low-text table:
+     - `H√∂ren` ‚Äî hear
+     - `Sprechen` ‚Äî speak
+     - `Lesen` ‚Äî read
+     - `Schreiben` ‚Äî write
+   - Use icons: ear, mouth, eye, pen.
+
+3. **Adipoli path**
+   - Text only:
+     ```text
+     Watch ‚Üí Listen ‚Üí Say ‚Üí Check ‚Üí Fix
+     ```
+   - No full roadmap.
+
+4. **First identity line**
+   - Visual: notebook/phone input.
+   - Text: `Ich lerne Deutsch.` / `I am learning German.`
+   - Practice pause graphic: `Say it aloud.`
+
+5. **Reason choice**
+   - Visual: five simple chips.
+   - Text: `Goethe A1`, `Germany plan`, `Family`, `Work/Ausbildung`, `Confidence`.
+   - Learner says one reason in English/Manglish.
+
+6. **Must-do vs booster**
+   - Two-card comparison.
+   - Must-do: `answer 5 greetings`.
+   - Booster: `shadow 10 more lines`.
+
+7. **Closed check**
+   - Text: `No notes. Find the weak spot.`
+   - Keep calm, not exam-scary.
+
+### AI image prompt
+
+Adult Malayali beginner at a Kerala home-study desk, opening a phone-first Goethe A1 German course app, serious warm exam-prep mood, small notebook with one clear phrase card area, no readable fake text, no mascot, premium educational illustration, low clutter, no childish cartoon style.
+
+### Phone-friendly editing notes
+
+- Keep path graphic on screen under 20 seconds.
+- Put Boss talking-head beside or above one card, not over a dense slide.
+- Cut any long Germany/migration motivational speech.
+
